<h2>About Revenue Grader</h2>

<p>Revenue Grader is a diagnostic tool developed and managed by Revenue Architects. The diagnostic is designed to help revenue-marketing leaders rapidly assess their revenue performance potential and develop a top-level prioritized plan. Revenue Grader takes a broad and strategic view across integrated marketing best practices to help managers identify and assess the critical elements of revenue performance.</p>
<p>The diagnostic is structured across three layers:</p>
<ul>
<li>Revenue Strategy Layer – capabilities to deliver competitive advantage and build a prioritized revenue marketing plan</li>
<li>Revenue Systems Layer – the revenue organization, website. apps and social media presence and technologies including marketing automation and CRM</li>
<li>Revenue Programs Layer – the ability to envision, design, integrate, launch and measure marketing and sales campaigns.</li>
<p>
We hope the diagnostic will help you identify priorities in your business and serve as a starting point for your integrated marketing strategy and plan.
</p>

<h4>How does it work?</h4>

<p>After a user registers, they are provided access to a 50-dimension diagnostic tool. The user rates maturity on key factors using a scale of 1-5. For each dimension, they can choose to “add to plan” and indicate priority level.  The result is a prioritized top-level plan with “must do”, “should do” and “could do” items.</p>

<h4>Key features:</h4>

<p>50 best practice dimensions across Revenue Strategy, Revenue Systems and Revenue Programs with explanatory text.
1-5 capability maturity scoring engine with weighted scoring
Ability to “add to plan” and rate priority using “must”, “should”, “could”
Ability to view the report and sort by maturity and priority factors
Save and return to the plan</p>


